 a November treat for theme-lovers – a slew of new free themes by Automattic designers and theme wranglers have made their debut on WordPress.org. Meet the fabulous five: Crafted by Caroline Moore, Affinity features an elegant multi-panel scrolling front page. Geared to weddings and family announcements, it&#8217;s flexible enough to suit a wide &#8230; <a href="https://themeshaper.com/2016/11/07/theme-o-rama/" class="more-link">Continue reading<span class="screen-reader-text"> "Theme-o-rama"</span></a><img alt="" border="0" src="https://pixel.wp.com/b.gif?host=themeshaper.com&#038;blog=45531309&#038;post=6674&#038;subd=themeshaper&#038;ref=&#038;feed=1" width="1" height="1" />";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:10:"Kathryn P.";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:9843:"<p>We have a November treat for theme-lovers – a slew of new free themes by Automattic designers and theme wranglers have made their debut on WordPress.org. Meet the fabulous five:</p>\n<p>Crafted by<a href="http://carolinemoore.net/"> Caroline Moore</a>,<a href="https://wordpress.org/themes/affinity/"><strong> Affinity</strong></a> features an elegant multi-panel scrolling front page. Geared to weddings and family announcements, it&#8217;s flexible enough to suit a wide variety of sites.</p>\n<p><a href="https://affinitydemo.wordpress.com/"><img data-attachment-id="6688" data-permalink="https://themeshaper.com/2016/11/07/theme-o-rama/affinity-ss-compact/" data-orig-file="https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/affinity-ss-compact.jpg?w=840&#038;h=883" data-orig-size="1665,1751" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}" data-image-title="" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/affinity-ss-compact.jpg?w=840&#038;h=883?w=285" data-large-file="https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/affinity-ss-compact.jpg?w=840&#038;h=883?w=840" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-6688" src="https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/affinity-ss-compact.jpg?w=840&#038;h=883" alt="Affinity screenshot" width="840" height="883" srcset="https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/affinity-ss-compact.jpg?w=840&amp;h=883 840w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/affinity-ss-compact.jpg?w=143&amp;h=150 143w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/affinity-ss-compact.jpg?w=285&amp;h=300 285w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/affinity-ss-compact.jpg?w=768&amp;h=808 768w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/affinity-ss-compact.jpg?w=974&amp;h=1024 974w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/affinity-ss-compact.jpg 1665w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 1362px) 62vw, 840px" /></a></p>\n<p><a href="https://thomasguillot.com/">Thomas Guillot</a> designed <a href="https://wordpress.org/themes/shoreditch/"><strong>Shoreditch</strong></a> especially for businesses who want to easily combine multiple panels on any page.</p>\n<p><a href="https://shoreditchdemo.wordpress.com/"><img data-attachment-id="6685" data-permalink="https://themeshaper.com/2016/11/07/theme-o-rama/shoreditch-ss/" data-orig-file="https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/shoreditch-ss.jpg?w=840&#038;h=959" data-orig-size="720,822" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/shoreditch-ss.jpg?w=840&#038;h=959?w=263" data-large-file="https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/shoreditch-ss.jpg?w=840&#038;h=959?w=720" class="alignnone wp-image-6685" src="https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/shoreditch-ss.jpg?w=840&#038;h=959" alt="Shoreditch screenshot" width="840" height="959" srcset="https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/shoreditch-ss.jpg 720w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/shoreditch-ss.jpg?w=131&amp;h=150 131w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/shoreditch-ss.jpg?w=263&amp;h=300 263w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 1362px) 62vw, 840px" /></a></p>\n<p>Looking for a fresh new blogging-focussed theme? Check out our trio:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>A modern blogging theme that shows off gorgeous photography, <a href="https://wordpress.org/themes/revelar/"><strong>Revelar</strong></a> is designed by <a href="http://mutelife.com/">Filipe Varela</a> and developed by <a href="https://soakingupthelight.wordpress.com/">Ola Bodera</a>;</li>\n<li><a href="http://diaryofawebsite.com/">Tammie Lister</a>&#8216;s <strong><a href="https://wordpress.org/themes/cols/">Cols</a></strong> features a minimalist multi-column text display; and</li>\n<li><strong><a href="https://wordpress.org/themes/lyretail/">Lyretail</a>,</strong> designed by <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/melchoyce/">Mel Choyce</a> and developed by Caroline Moore, is a clean single-column theme for personal bloggers with prominent social links in the header.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Take your favorite for a spin today!</p>\n<p><a href="https://revelardemo.wordpress.com/"><img data-attachment-id="6690" data-permalink="https://themeshaper.com/2016/11/07/theme-o-rama/revelar-ss-2/" data-orig-file="https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/revelar-ss1.png?w=840&#038;h=630" data-orig-size="720,540" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/revelar-ss1.png?w=840&#038;h=630?w=300" data-large-file="https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/revelar-ss1.png?w=840&#038;h=630?w=720" class="imgborder alignnone wp-image-6690" src="https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/revelar-ss1.png?w=840&#038;h=630" alt="Revelar screenshot" width="840" height="630" srcset="https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/revelar-ss1.png 720w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/revelar-ss1.png?w=150&amp;h=113 150w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/revelar-ss1.png?w=300&amp;h=225 300w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 1362px) 62vw, 840px" /></a></p>\n<p><a href="https://colsdemo.wordpress.com/"><img data-attachment-id="6691" data-permalink="https://themeshaper.com/2016/11/07/theme-o-rama/cols-ss-2/" data-orig-file="https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/11/cols-ss.png?w=840&#038;h=630" data-orig-size="880,660" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&q